TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DIM_CUSTOMERS.CUST_KEY as CUST_KEY, DIM_CUSTOMERS.MD5_CHECKSUM as MD5_CHECKSUM, DIM_CUSTOMERS.CUST_CODE as CUST_CODE FROM DIM_CUSTOMERS where CUST_EFF_TO = '12-12-9999'

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: MD5(CUST_CODE||CUST_FIRST_NAME||CUST_LAST_NAME||CUST_GENDER||TO_CHAR(CUST_YEAR_OF_BIRTH)||CUST_MARITAL_STATUS||CUST_STREET_ADDRESS||CUST_POSTAL_CODE || CUST_CITY || CUST_STATE_PROVINCE || COUNTRY_CODE || CUST_MAIN_PHONE_NUMBER || CUST_INCOME_LEVEL || TO_CHAR(CUST_CREDIT_LIMIT) || CUST_EMAIL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: MD5_checksum
